        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Flood Insurance Flexibility Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the National Flood Insurance Program (NFIP) to refund the appropriate amount of the premiums paid for flood insurance coverage if an insured cancels an NFIP policy and obtains non-NFIP coverage.</p>]]>
        </text>
